{"tid":685770,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[走數可恥]之前咪有個傻鳩話講個巴士站佢就去打卡","createTime":"2018-05-31T16:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T05:42:40.000Z","uid":5399,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"87c90b472613072d576e22277f18e0757ac68b30","tid":685770,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"唔知仲有冇巴打記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實果個就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚟緊放假,希望可以每日去至少一個地方, 順便喺附近影下相<br />\n睇下一個月可以去幾多個地方<br />\n順便學下影相, 唔洗日日屌死氣喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第十一站 #17 <blockquote>堅離地城</blockquote>(堅尼地城)<br />\n搭巴士出發<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/001636_f5e131b295e5bd854d979c79f4684ea2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F001636_f5e131b295e5bd854d979c79f4684ea2.jpg&h=ee48121d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/001641_999c8bd0d8f47a287e0442b50ed0b3d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F001641_999c8bd0d8f47a287e0442b50ed0b3d4.jpg&h=fbad94a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/001646_166e6f6c921e48ecf8ecf17cb9c21722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F001646_166e6f6c921e48ecf8ecf17cb9c21722.jpg&h=b898af36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/001753_9a7739463661b73bc56e9006bc50ce72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F001753_9a7739463661b73bc56e9006bc50ce72.jpg&h=80ffb0d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da9364af3503523d49460de4aef8fd9defc82019","tid":685770,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike"