244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F002337_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=123f7588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前幾日同fd去咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"都唔係影個巴士站 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再去過啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7377e87a55c6fa91cd98aaf047299bcb41f173aa","tid":685770,"uid":5399,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/002456_8cf887b53ae0678714460399d5fec0f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F002456_8cf887b53ae0678714460399d5fec0f8.jpg&h=89fc6753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺到講番聲先, 因為個鏡頭唔啱用, 有啲相crop唔到我會由得佢黑角<br />\n唔好屌我mk懶係野整黑隻角, 冇心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/002607_47ca18e0ded21bd9f64c09d48b2d95f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F002607_47ca18e0ded21bd9f64c09d48b2d95f5.jpg&h=74effb83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便估下我點過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efe19239dda025dfe0277cf4fac51cbaa2b9d0a","tid":685770,"uid":172879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"[img]圖片網址[/img]"},{"pid":"f2ca3577d1cdff2329d3c21891779af5983ac354","tid":685770,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n堅尼地城原為石塘咀以西的卑路乍灣（古稱「垃圾灣」），是港島最早的「城中城」，早於1886年已經開始發展，堅尼地城填海計劃是著名商人遮打（Catchick Paul Chater, 1846-1926）發起，港英第七任總督堅尼地（Arthur Edward Kennedy，1872-1877在任）任內開始建設，今天的吉席街和堅尼地城就是為了紀念二人而命名。<br />\n<br />\n堅尼地城最早期的對外巴士路線，是於1939年7月1日開辦的中巴5A線，在爹核士街泊街，但日治期間停駛。國共內戰期間區內人口迅速增加，1948年11月1日中巴5號線延長至至爹核士街，在陳李濟藥廠（卑路乍街及爹核士街交界處，已重建成「聚賢逸居」）外泊街；同年12月16日5A也恢復正常服務，而中巴其後於60年代開辦21線往返堅尼地城及摩星嶺，亦同樣在該藥廠附近設置總站。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hkbus.wikia.com/wiki/%E5%A0%85%E5%B0%BC%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%8E%E7%B8%BD%E7%AB%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkbus.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A0%2585%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25AB%2599&d=22rjw7MZQzEBVDU82dJsoACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f6ae19ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkbus.wikia.com/wiki/%E5%A0%85%E5%B0%BC%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%8E%E7%B8%BD%E7%AB%99</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/003215_b499d20d8185e5ddb42cba431abd8adb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F003215_b499d20d8185e5ddb42cba431abd8adb.jpg&h=7817c696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新巴同城巴都有房仔比員工休息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/003242_83a4485e3182a55ccccba9b48695e722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F003242_83a4485e3182a55ccccba9b48695e722.jpg&h=2be74800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/003309_cb5109c56f79e2c1f17838bf96413922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F003309_cb5109c56f79e2c1f17838bf96413922.jpg&h=7d3bef57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然冇乜車, 不過總站出面啲車都係亂咁擺"},{"pid":"e2314376897afa6035e5f3555a808cb04d27afbb","tid":685770,"uid":5399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/003503_6b7c2b23d9cd64f72d2e5fd75c2941ff.JP